sources.title: Girl O' My Dreams (1934) MARY CARLISLE ♥ LON CHANEY JR
sources.description:
Stars: Mary Carlisle, Lon Chaney, Jr, Sterling Holloway
Director: Ray McCarey

A conceited college track star, used to being a "big man on campus", gets a jolt when he loses an election to see who is the most popular man in the school. A young Lon (Creighton) Chaney Jr. steals the show!

sources.title: Girl O' My Dreams (1934) Comedy, Drama Full Length Movie
sources.description:
A festival of fun, high-jinks and college capers...The Love Story of Young America! 
A conceited college track star, used to being "big man on campus", gets a jolt when he loses an election to see who is the most popular man in the school.

Director: Ray McCarey
Writer: George Waggner
Stars: Mary Carlisle, Sterling Holloway, Edward J. Nugent
Genres: Classics, Comedy, Drama
